reviewText: Its okay. I would have liked to see more...

This was just amazing! The production values are so far above what I would expect to find here... I just can't describe! The cinematography, the lush mid-century modern setting, the music and the beautiful model all combine to create an immersive, almost hypnotic experience. It's beautiful, sensual and mesmerizing. There's nothing prurient about this, but it is a playful and seductive tease that you'll want to watch over and over. If you love the mid-century modern period, as I do, this is more eye candy than you could ever expect in one video. Bravo!
